{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b The wedge.} None of the cloud PMS vendors have a {\b token economy} or {\b multi-method local payment} architecture. Wellness chains and resort properties that want prepaid packages (very common in Thailand: "10-massage card", "weekly yoga unlimited") cannot get this from Cloudbeds without custom dev. VBWD ships it.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Local payment rails (must support)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b PromptPay} (QR-based bank transfer, dominant for under-THB-5,000 payments)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b TrueMoney Wallet} (e-wallet, common with younger Thai buyers)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Rabbit LinePay} (LINE-integrated wallet)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Visa/MasterCard via Stripe Thailand (live), Omise (popular Thai gateway), 2C2P (regional)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab PayPal (low usage but expected for international guests)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Plugin status today:} Stripe + PayPal + YooKassa in core. {\b PromptPay + TrueMoney = a plugin to ship}, ~30 hrs of work, sellable at \u8364 ?99\u8211-199 one-time.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Local agency landscape (the channel)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The reseller play depends on convincing 3\u8211-5 Thai dev/web agencies to add VBWD to their offering. Real candidates (publicly visible, well-known in BKK tech scene):\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Pomelo Software} \u8212- Bangkok, hospitality-tech focused\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Seven Peaks Software} \u8212- Bangkok, larger consultancy with hotel clients\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Codium / Codigo} \u8212- boutique Thai dev shops\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Tigerbay} \u8212- Phuket-based, digital agency with hotel clients\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Fastwork-listed mid-tier dev shops} (~50 active hotel-website builders on the platform)\sa180\par}
