{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Wellness pitch one-liner\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li720 \fi0 "Your spa, your bookings, your loyalty cards \u8212- on your domain, in your customers' language and currency, with prepaid packages and memberships. No per-booking commission. \u8364 ?499/year."\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Reuse the existing hotel deck ({\f1 decks/hotel/}) as the structural template, swap "rooms" for "treatments" and "OTAs" for "third-party booking apps". One designer-hour of work. Ship as {\f1 decks/wellness/}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Wellness Y1 revenue inside the geo numbers\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Already counted in the per-geo tables above. The reason wellness numbers are conservative: {\b the agencies are the bottleneck}, not the demand. With 8\u8211-15 agencies recruited in Y1, they each onboard 3\u8211-8 wellness clients in Y1 \u8212- that ceiling is what caps the number.\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 8. Channel-led distribution (no founder calls \u8212- the "respect the constraint" section)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 The entire geo plan dies if you take a single Zoom call. Every channel below is async-by-design.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Channel A \u8212- Cold email to local agencies (one-shot, no call)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 30 agencies per geo (90 total), pulled from LinkedIn + Tech in Asia + ArabNet + local dev directories.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab One-paragraph pitch, {\b personalised by name + agency website + one specific hotel/spa client they shipped}.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Pitch shape: "I've built a self-hosted hospitality platform that you can resell to your hotel/spa clients under your own brand. Pro license \u8364 ?1,499/yr, Enterprise \u8364 ?4,999/yr with white-label. You charge the client \u8364 ?200\u8211-500/mo. Demo + docs + reseller pack: [link]. No call needed \u8212- everything is in the link."\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Hard rule}: if the agency replies asking for a call, send the demo URL + the YouTube walkthrough + a Calendly-free async-feedback form. If they insist on a call, decline politely: "I'm solo and async-only; if the docs and demo aren't enough I'm probably the wrong vendor."\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Expected conversion: 2\u8211-5 reseller signups per geo from a 30-email batch.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Time cost: 4 hrs research + 4 hrs writing per geo = 24 hrs total. One burst weekend.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Channel B \u8212- Hire one local part-time freelancer per geo\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is the single biggest unlock for the geo plan and the only paid expense.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Per geo}: hire 1 freelancer for {\b \u8364 ?300\u8211-\u8364 ?500/month} (rates are realistic in TH/VN; closer to \u8364 ?700 in UAE/KSA).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Their job (async-only, async-reporting, monthly Loom updates):\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Translate landing page + key admin strings to local language\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Be the local face on local forums (Pantip Thailand, Vietnamese tech FB groups, Saudi Telegram)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Triage local-language inbound to Discord\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Write 1 blog post/month in local language targeting local search terms\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Optionally: build the local payment rail plugin (paid as one-shot project on top of retainer)\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Where to find them}: Upwork (still works for this), local marketplaces (Fastwork TH, Freelancer.vn, Bawabba SA), Twitter/X dev community, Discord\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Total monthly cost across 3 geos: {\b \u8364 ?1,000\u8211-\u8364 ?1,500}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Important: this is the {\i only} place the plan trades cash for time.} It's worth it because each freelancer-hour replaces a founder-hour you don't have.\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Channel C \u8212- Self-hosted directory / marketplace listings (already in plan 01)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Cloudron, Coolify, Easypanel, Awesome-selfhosted listings cover the global self-hoster audience including SE Asia tinkerers and Saudi engineers. {\b Already in plan 01 weeks 11\u8211-12. No change.}\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Channel D \u8212- Regional content SEO (long-tail compounder)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 1 article per month in English targeting:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab "Cloudbeds alternative Thailand"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab "self-hosted hotel booking engine"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab "Hotelogix vs [X]"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab "ezCloud alternative Vietnam English"\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab "spa management software UAE Arabic"\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Plus 1 article per month in {\b local language} written by the local freelancer (Channel B)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab 12-month outcome: 24 articles total, 3\u8211-6 of which rank top-10 on long-tail keywords \u8594 ? 50\u8211-200 monthly organic visits on each = compounding inbound that {\b never asks you for a call}\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Channel E \u8212- Local conferences (no attendance, content only)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Skip physical attendance (time + travel = blows the constraint).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab BUT: write a content piece per major regional event ("3 things missing from this year's HITEC Asia / Future Hospitality Riyadh / VITM Hanoi"). Tag the speakers/exhibitors. Some will reply. Async ROI.\sa180\par}
